  "datePublished": "2026-04-02",
  "description": "The position of inheriting, continuing, and transforming a tradition without either renewing it wholesale or abandoning it — occupied by every living person but systematically eliminated by settler colonialism, genring, and binary nationalist frameworks that offer only the 'traditional' or the 'assimilated' position.",
